resit pengakuan, tuan.

227
00:12:51,067 --> 00:12:53,033
Dan mungkin menambah
media sosial anda?

228
00:12:53,167 --> 00:12:54,433
Hanya bergurau!

229
00:12:54,567 --> 00:12:58,033
